column5: Could anyone recommend a spot for me to park my boat for the remainder of the season? 16.5ft aluminum.  I prefer Callander Bay or South Bay, although in between would be perfect.  Thanks
Ask at the marina at the end of Landsdowne St. in Calander. On the left before the dock. Maybe the yacht club in Calander?

Not sure of the marina's name but it is at the end of the road at Wade's Landing near the village of Nipissing. I like it there cause you are behind the islands and sheltered when you can't get out on the main lake.  Rob C
Rob might be referring to Nipissing Lodge. Their website says $15/day to dock I believe.
